<h2>How We Test</h2>
<p>Each AI design tool was evaluated on: design quality, ease of use, AI feature accuracy, template/library depth, export options, collaboration features, and value for money. Tests included real-world scenarios like creating social media graphics, designing brand identities, prototyping app interfaces, and generating custom imagery from text prompts.</p>
